# Triangle Information GUI

## Overview
This program allows the user to create a triangle by clicking three points on the screen.
After creating the triangle, the program calculates and displays the area of the triangle.

## How to Use
1. Run the program.
2. Click three points on the screen to form a triangle.
3. The program will display the area of the triangle.
4. Close the window by clicking anywhere after viewing the result.

